### **4. 32_LiveStreamGrid**  
**Description:**  
Visualizes streaming numeric data in real time using a responsive grid-based chart.

#### **README.md**
```markdown
# LiveStreamGrid - Real-Time Data Plotting Tool

LiveStreamGrid is a live visualization tool for metrics, simulations, and any numeric input flow.

## Features
- Realtime chart  
- Auto-scroll history  
- Adjustable refresh rate  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/32_LiveStreamGrid.git
cd 32_LiveStreamGrid
python visualize.py
